- `font-mono` - Data, addresses (IBM Plex Mono)

### Layouts

- `arcade-cabinet` - Game machine frame
- `arcade-screen` - CRT monitor
- `crt-content` - Content inside CRT
- `pacman-dots` - Dot pattern background
- `perspective-grid` - 3D grid background

